README for OpenWrt_NXT_Server

What it is
==========

OpenWrt_NXT_Server is a LEGO(R) MINDSTORMS(R) NXT 2.0 server package
for OpenWrt (https://openwrt.org).

It listens on UDP port 35000. When command received, it executes it
on NXT and sends response (if any) back.


LEGO and MINDSTORMS are trademarks of the LEGO Group.


